	 exceeding the ticket limit will have their orders canceled at the venue's
	 discretion. All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges. Mobile barcodes
	 delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the right to change d
	elivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have a ticket r
	egardless of age. No babies in arms. No Elevator. Ramps only to the balcon
	y level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive early. No weapons. 
